title: Adidas WRISTBAND Large x4
description:
Description:

  • Absorbent wristbands designed for players who aim to conquer the court. Ideal for intense matches like five-setters and tie-breaks, these wristbands help you stay dry and comfortable.

Key Features:

  • Maximized comfort through material construction and thickness.
  • Embroidered adidas Badge of Sport on the front for a stylish touch.

Materials:

  • 38% Cotton
  • 35% Polyacrylics
  • 24% Polyester
  • 3% Elastodiene
  • Plain knit fabric

Usage:

  • Suitable for tennis players and other athletes who need to manage sweat during intense activities.
